SUMMARY:Deadline: Beca Plataforma Bogota: Arte\, Ciencia y Tecnologia 2026 
 (Colombia residents only)
DESCRIPTION:Plataforma Bogota\, Idartes' art\, science and technology media
  lab\, awards four grants of COP 12\,000\,000 each to run interactive labs
  combining art\, science\, and technology. ELIGIBILITY: Colombian citizens
  or foreigners legally resident in Bogota only. Deadline 24 August 2026.\n
 \nOrganisation: Idartes / Plataforma Bogota\nLocation: Bogota\, Colombia. 
 Colombian citizens or foreigners legally resident in Bogota only.\nAward: 
 4 grants of COP 12\,000\,000 each (approx. EUR 2\,700) to run interactive 
 art + science + technology labs at Plataforma Bogota. No application fee.\
